snippet.title: A Space for the Unbound - Now Available for PC and Consoles!
snippet.description:
OUT NOW ON PC AND CONSOLES!

Follow the journey of the high school sweethearts, Atma and Raya in uncovering secrets of supernatural events occurring in a town inspired by 90s Indonesia in Mojiken Studio's latest adventure game, A Space For The Unbound.

- - - - -

Developer: Mojiken Studio, Toge Productions
Publisher: Toge Productions, ChorusWorldwide

- - - - -

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1201270/A_Space_for_the_Unbound/
GOG: https://www.gog.com/en/game/a_space_for_the_unbound
EGS: https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/a-space-for-the-unbound-57e666
Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/a-space-for-the-unbound-switch/
PS: https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10005843
Xbox: https://www.xbox.com/id-ID/games/store/a-space-for-the-unbound/9PG2RZ8GVZCJ

- - - - -
